data.description: NEW ROOF  & GUTTERS! This beautiful well kept home is located on a corner lot in Williamson Farms Gated Community. It has 3 Beds, 2 Bath, Office + Storm Shelter! Large living room has LVP wood flooring, built-in book shelf and gas fireplace with wood mantel. Spacious Office that could also be used as a Game Room. The Kitchen has granite counter tops, breakfast bar, pantry, and window over the sink. The Primary Bedroom has two walk-in closets, private bathroom with jetted tub and separate shower. The split floor plan has 2nd Bedroom with walk-in closet, 3rd Bedroom with a spacious closet and a full Bathroom. Sprinkler system in the front and backyard.  Large front porch and extended back yard patio perfect for entertaining. Neighborhood amenities include Clubhouse, Family Pool, Adult Pool, Fishing Pond, Walking trail and Playground.
